org.gradle.api.logging.configuration

Enum ConsoleOutput

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ConsoleOutput>
      • org.gradle.api.logging.configuration.ConsoleOutput
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ConsoleOutput>

    @Incubating
public enum ConsoleOutput
extends Enum<ConsoleOutput>
    Specifies how to treat color and dynamic console output.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      Auto
      Enable color and rich output when the current process is attached to a console, disable when not attached to a console.
      Plain
      Disable all color and rich output.
      Rich
      Enable color and rich output, regardless of whether the current process is attached to a console or not.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • Plain

        public static final ConsoleOutput Plain
        Disable all color and rich output. Generate plain text only.

      • Auto

        public static final ConsoleOutput Auto
        Enable color and rich output when the current process is attached to a console, disable when not attached to a console.

      • Rich

        public static final ConsoleOutput Rich
        Enable color and rich output, regardless of whether the current process is attached to a console or not. When not attached to a console, the color and rich output is encoded using ANSI control characters.
